    <item>
      <title>研究人员在瓶装水中发现大量塑料颗粒</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/01/10/1223730333/bottled-water-plastic-microplastic-nanoplastic-study</link>
      <description><![CDATA[研究人员在一升瓶装水中发现了大约 240,000 个可检测到的塑料碎片。其中大多数是纳米塑料——尺寸小于 1 微米的颗粒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/01/10/1223730333/bottled-water-plastic-microplastic-nanoplastic-study</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:00:51 GMT</pubDate>
